We recommend for the municipality of Buug to:
Stop the transfer of funds from Trust Fund to General Fund relating to the amount due to the BIR;
Payment to BIR of tax withheld from suppliers must be sourced from the fund it was withheld;
Return all transferred fund from TF to GF which were not yet paid to BIR, if any; and
Review all entries made relative to the transfer and remittance to BIR and effect any adjustments to correct any misstatements in the financial statements.
